#: apps/badges/admin.py
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    WARNING: avoid configuration updates on activated badges.\n"
"                    Active badge templates are continuously processed and learners may already have progress on them.\n"
"                    Any changes in badge template requirements (including data rules) will affect learners' experience!\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    PERINGATAN: hindari pembaruan konfigurasi pada lencana yang sudah diaktifkan.\n"
"                    Template lencana aktif diproses secara terus-menerus dan peserta didik mungkin sudah memiliki kemajuan di dalamnya.\n"
"                    Setiap perubahan dalam persyaratan template lencana (termasuk aturan data) akan memengaruhi pengalaman peserta didik!\n"
"                    "

